or TEIform=\"author\">Posidipp.</author> </bibl>). </sense> <sense n=\"B\" id=\"n41633.4\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Med.\">Med.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">pour</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">throw over oneself,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">χύσιν δ᾽ ἐπεχεύατο φύλλων</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:5:487\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.487</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κατακλιθεὶς ἐπιχείσθω τὴν πέριξ ἄμμον</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Antyll.</author> </bibl> </cit> ap. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0722.tlg001:10:8:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Orib.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.8.4</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπεχεύατο πήχεε παιδί</foreign> she <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">threw her</tr_> arms <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">round</tr_> the boy, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:268\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.268</biblScope> </bibl> ; but <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πολλὴν ἐπεχεύατο ὕλην</quote_> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">for himself,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:5:257\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.257</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n41633.5\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"s